    "### Why This Tier Exists vs Earlier Tiers\n",
    "\n",
    "**Tier 6 (Autonomous Self-Optimizing Ecosystem)** provides distributed intelligence capabilities:\n",
    "- **Distributed Intelligence**: Multiple autonomous agents making local decisions\n",
    "- **Market Mechanism**: Contract Net Protocol for resource allocation\n",
    "- **Self-Organization**: Emergent coalition formation and market equilibrium\n",
    "- **Learning**: Individual agent adaptation through experience\n",
    "- **Robustness**: No single point of failure affects entire system\n",
    "- **Scalability**: Handles large terminal operations efficiently\n",
    "\n",
    "### Pros vs Cons\n",
    "\n",
    "**Advantages:**\n",
    "- No single point of failure can crash the entire system\n",
    "- Autonomous decision making without central coordination\n",
    "- Market-based resource allocation ensures efficient utilization\n",
    "- Self-organizing behavior adapts to changing conditions\n",
    "- Learning agents improve performance over time\n",
    "- Emergent intelligence discovers optimal patterns\n",
    "\n",
    "**Disadvantages:**\n",
